content: Freytes: Focused on adding substantial new features to the `elizaos/spartan` repository, merging four significant pull requests. Their most impactful contributions included introducing a new Chrome extension in PR #17 (+42042 lines) and a Farcaster miniapp in PR #19 (+13210 lines). Freytes also improved the developer experience by adding Docker support for an easier development setup in PR #20. In total, their work added over 67k lines of new code and tests to build out major new components for the project.
